1. *Njihove* deca su veoma talentovana. (Their children are very talented.)
2. Oni zaista vole *njihove* porodice. (They really love their families.)
3. Nisam znao za *njihove* planove. (I didn't know about their plans.)
4. *Njihova* skupština je održana pre par dana. (Their assembly was held a few days ago.)
5. Oni su izgubili *njihove* stvari. (They lost their things.)
6. *Njihov* dom je veoma lep. (Their home is very beautiful.)
7. Oni se trude da zaštite *njihove* interese. (They try to protect their interests.)
8. *Njihov* nacin života je izmenjen. (Their way of life has changed.)